Version: Prompt Template v3.2 vs v4.0

Metrics Measured:

Grammar accuracy

Faithfulness to original meaning

Creativity / stylistic variation

User approval (via scoring)


Outcome Summary:

v4.0 achieved 18% fewer meaning distortions.

Slightly more verbose but improved flow.

No hallucinations observed in either version.

Users preferred v4.0 in 72% of blind tests.


Recommendation:
Deploy template v4.0 to production, reserve v3.2 as fallback.
